{"type": "article", "id": 17783, "title": "威士忌包装", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-19T06:30:14Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 38, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607104226AsWx901eB4hI7KR2.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是爱丁堡的设计事务所 Contagious 设计的威士忌酒瓶，还另配有两个玻璃杯和托盘。酒瓶的外形源于一滴泪珠，因为所盛的酒已在黑暗中酝酿了 75 年，酒瓶的表面有 75 道旋转的条带纹路，让这瓶酒显得晶莹而珍贵。从正中心向下看，这款威士忌酒顺着螺旋纹呈现出深浅不同的颜色变化，非常漂亮。玻璃杯和托盘上都有相应的纹路，略带凹凸，让人情不自禁去触摸。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104225G0y3DLNdSv6VEMkh.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.91078067\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016060710422583GgWE2OZRrdaAhv.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.87918216\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104226ynNDjuTopvCHfR8t.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"2.07620818\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}